    "body": "This adds coverage for when [BlockWaitOptions](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/node/mining_types.h#L94-L113)'s `feeThreshold` is set to `MAX_MONEY`. In other words, when the IPC client is only interested in tip updates, not in fee increases.\r\n\r\nThis tested ended up in #33922 at some point  https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/33922#issuecomment-3674495132, but doesn't really belong there.",
